Building on a history of technological innovation, AV designs, develops, produces, and supports an advanced portfolio of Unmanned Aircraft Systems (UAS) and efficient electric energy systems.  The company's are used extensively by agencies of the U.S. Department of Defense and increasingly by allied military services to provide situational awareness to tactical operating units through reliable, real-time, airborne reconnaissance, surveillance, and target acquisition.  AV's efficient energy systems include for increasing the productivity of industrial electric vehicles, and for clean energy generation on buildings.  More information about AV is available at www.avinc.com.
