Exhibit 10.1
 
The purpose of the AeroVironment, Inc. 2006 Equity Incentive Plan (the "") is to promote the success and enhance the value of AeroVironment, Inc. (the "") by linking the personal interests of the members of the Board, Employees, and Consultants to those of Company stockholders and by providing such individuals with an incentive for outstanding performance to generate superior returns to Company stockholders. The Plan is further intended to provide flexibility to the Company in its ability to motivate, attract, and retain the services of members of the Board, Employees, and Consultants upon whose judgment, interest, and special effort the successful conduct of the Company's operation is largely dependent.
Plan
Company
 
