ABOUT AEROVIRONMENT, INC.
 
AeroVironment is a technology solutions provider that designs, develops, produces and supports an advanced portfolio of (UAS) and electric transportation solutions.  Agencies of the U.S. Department of Defense and allied military services use the company's electric-powered, extensively to provide situational awareness to tactical operating units through real-time, airborne reconnaissance, surveillance and communication. 
