AeroVironment is a technology solutions provider that designs, develops, produces, supports and operates an advanced portfolio of (UAS) and electric transportation solutions.  Agencies of the U.S. Department of Defense and allied military services use AeroVironment's electric-powered, extensively to provide situational awareness to tactical operating units through real-time, airborne reconnaissance, surveillance and communication.  AeroVironment's electric transportation solutions include a comprehensive suite of for consumers, automakers, utilities and government agencies, for EV developers and for commercial fleets.  More information about AeroVironment is available at .
